      "source": "void binary_string(int n){\r\n    int pos_case = (int)Math.pow(2,n);\r\n    for (int i =0; i<pos_case; i++){\r\n        String s = int_to_binary_string(i,n);\r\n        System.out.println(s);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\nbinary_string(3);",
