      "source": "// int n =3;\r\n// int[] incomplete_str = new int[n];\r\n// int pos;\r\npublic void print_all_binary_string(int n, int[] incomplete_str, int pos){\r\n    if (pos ==n){\r\n        System.out.println(Arrays.toString(incomplete_str));\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    else{\r\n        // incomplete_str[pos] = 0;\r\n        // print_all_binary_string(n, incomplete_str, pos+1);\r\n        // incomplete_str[pos] = 1;\r\n        // print_all_binary_string(n, incomplete_str, pos+1);\r\n        for(int i =0; i<=1; i++){\r\n            incomplete_str[pos] = i;\r\n            print_all_binary_string(n, incomplete_str, pos+1);\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n// public static void main(String[] args){\r\n//     int n = 3;\r\n//     int[] arr = new int[n];\r\n//     print_all_binary_string(n, arr, -1);\r\n// }\r\n\r\npublic void print_all_bin_str(int n){\r\n    int[] arr = new int[n];\r\n    print_all_binary_string(n, arr, 0);\r\n}\r\n\r\n    print_all_bin_str(3);\r\n\r\n\r\n",
