      "id": "a7673d44-5c2e-4973-b1f9-e8bd537ed20e",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Example 3: Print all subsets of {1, 2, … n}\n\nExample: n = 3\n{}\n{1}\n{2}\n{3}\n{1, 2}\n{2, 3}\n{1, 3}\n{1, 2, 3}",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
